SUMMARY:Floral Design Program: Designing with Lilies\, Tropicals & Orchids
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to unleash your creativity with lilies\, tropicals & orchids in this hands-on floral design class. These are truly special flowers for design\, each having unique characteristics that offer something special for designers. Explore the history of these flowers and key horticultural characteristics\, including their diverse colours\, forms\, and textures. You will also learn how to create outstanding traditional and contemporary arrangements.\n \nPrerequisites: Classic Design Fundamentals I &II. Learn more about our Certificate in Floral Design\n \nWednesdays\, April 1\, 8\, 15\, 22\, 6 to 9 p.m.\nPublic $240\, Members $190 (plus applicable taxes and fees)\n \nRegistration Deadline: Friday\, March 27 at 12:00 PM.\n \nPlease note: Course fees do not include flowers or supplies. Students are encouraged to find a local flower shop or grocery store to purchase their flowers. A materials list will be e-mailed prior to the start of each class.\n\n\nAbout Lil Taggart\nLil Taggart is an experienced and creative designer and instructor in Floral Arts. She is also an accredited Floral Design Judge and has competed on an international level as well as domestically. She serves on the board of Canada Blooms\, co-chairs the staging for the Toronto Flower Show\, is past president of the Georgetown Horticultural society and is a member of The Garden Club of Toronto. \nAdditional Program Information\n\nPlease review our Refund Policy and Terms of Agreement.\nFor more information on accessibility at the garden please review our Accessibility Features webpage. If you have any accessibility requirements during your program please email programsupport@torontobotanicalgarden.ca.\nTo learn more about the Toronto Botanical Garden and our programs\, please review our list of Frequently Asked Questions.
URL:https://torontobotanicalgarden.ca/event/floral-design-program-designing-with-lilies-tropicals-orchids-2/
LOCATION:Toronto Botanical Garden\, 777 Lawrence Ave E\, Toronto\, ON\, M3C 1P2\, Canada
CATEGORIES:Floral Design
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://torontobotanicalgarden.ca/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/0f71a9043dfcd69183089ee05a7ce3d6.jpg
END:VEVENT
